{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Gatsby v2 introduces <code class=\"language-text\">StaticQuery</code>, a new API that allows components to retrieve data via GraphQL query.</p>\n<p><em>Note: There is <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues/6350\">a known issue with <code class=\"language-text\">StaticQuery</code></a> that only allows it to work with non-page components as seen in the example below. Until <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/issues/6350\">#6350</a> is resolved, page queries should be performed <a href=\"https://next.gatsbyjs.org/docs/build-a-page-with-graphql-query/\">as seen in this article</a>.</em></p>\n<h2 id=\"basic-example\"><a href=\"#basic-example\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Basic example</h2>\n<p>Weâ€™ll create a new <code class=\"language-text\">Header</code> component located at <code class=\"language-text\">src/components/header.js</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\">\n      <pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> StaticQuery<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> graphql <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Header</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>StaticQuery\n    query<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>graphql<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n      query {\n        site {\n          siteMetadata {\n            title\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    `</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    render<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>site<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>siteMetadata<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>title<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> Header</code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>Using <code class=\"language-text\">StaticQuery</code>, you can colocate a component with its data. No longer is it required to, say, pass data down from <code class=\"language-text\">Layout</code> to <code class=\"language-text\">Header</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"typechecking\"><a href=\"#typechecking\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Typechecking</h2>\n<p>With the above pattern, you lose the ability to typecheck with PropTypes. To regain typechecking while achieving the same result, you can change the component to:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"jsx\">\n      <pre class=\"language-jsx\"><code class=\"language-jsx\"><span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> React <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"react\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> StaticQuery <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"gatsby\"</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> PropTypes <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"prop-types\"</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Header</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> data <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>site<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>siteMetadata<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>title<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>h1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>header</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> props <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>StaticQuery\n    query<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>graphql<span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`\n      query {\n        site {\n          siteMetadata {\n            title\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    `</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    render<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>Header</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">data</span><span class=\"token script language-javascript\"><span class=\"token script-punctuation punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token spread\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">...</span><span class=\"token attr-value\">props</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/></span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nHeader<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>propTypes <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  data<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> PropTypes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    site<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> PropTypes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      siteMetadata<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> PropTypes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">shape</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> PropTypes<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>string<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isRequired<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isRequired<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isRequired<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>isRequired<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<h2 id=\"how-it-differs-from-page-query\"><a href=\"#how-it-differs-from-page-query\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How it differs from page query</h2>\n<p>StaticQuery can do most of the things that page query can, including fragments.</p>\n<p>You canâ€™t, however, pass <strong>Query Variables</strong> to <code class=\"language-text\">StaticQuery</code>, like you can in page queries through <code class=\"language-text\">pageContext</code>.</p>","excerpt":"Gatsby v2 introduces  , a new API that allows components to retrieve data via GraphQL query. Note: There is  a known issue with   that onlyâ€¦","timeToRead":2,"fields":{"slug":"/docs/static-query/","anchor":"static-query"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Querying data in components using StaticQuery"},"parent":{"__typename":"File","relativePath":"docs/static-query.md"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/docs/static-query/"}}